ritik der Urteilskraft" bietet Anknüpfungspunkte für den Gedanken, durch kollektives vernunftgeleitetes Handeln die objektiven Bedingungen des Handelns selbst aus Vernunft zu gestalten.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket AV  Philosophie 2005-2012z9783110347067oZDB-74-AKP0 cprintz978305005180240uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305005711840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050057118423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050057118.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GPHc2000d2014  aZDB-74-AKPc2005d2012